{"article_id":"CbQBI2uq0SaXyCaG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A reporter 's question about hydroxychloroquine led to a testy moment at Sunday 's White House briefing .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Anthony Fauci was asked his thoughts on the effectiveness of the anti-malaria drug","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"in treating coronavirus patients ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"and President Donald Trump interrupted","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"before the director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases could answer .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"\" He ' s answered that question 15 times , \"","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"said Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"who had spent much of the news conference","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"touting the drug 's potential .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Earlier in the day , Fauci did answer a question about hydroxychloroquine","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"when he was on CBS 's `` Face the Nation . ''","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"\" The data are really , just , at best , suggestive , \"","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"\" There have been cases","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that show","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"there may be an effect","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"and there are others","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"to show","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"there 's no effect .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"So , I think","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"in terms of science ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"I do n't think","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"we could definitively say","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"it works . \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Coronavirus live updates :","depth":4},{"id":26,"text":"US deaths near 10K ahead of 'hardest and saddest week '","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"Fauci and White House trade adviser Peter Navarro got in a heated argument Saturday over hydroxychloroquine ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"according to Axios and the New York Times .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"According to the reports ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Navarro brought in studies from trials overseas","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"that show","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"the drug ,","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"which is often used","depth":15},{"id":34,"text":"to treat malaria ,","depth":15},{"id":35,"text":"was working to combat coronavirus .","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"Fauci maintained","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"that there is still only anecdotal information","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"and that more rigorous studies need to be done","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"to see the true effect of the drug ,","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"according to the reports .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"Despite the two arguing about the drug as a treatment ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"the White House coronavirus task force has agreed to surge the supply of hydroxychloroquine to hot zones .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Fauci also conceded in an interview with Science magazine in mid-March","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"that he and Trump `` disagree on some things ''","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"but that the president listens","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"and `` goes his own way . ''","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Fauci at times has been absent from some of the briefings .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"When he 's not present ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"that sometimes fuels speculation about his relationship with Trump .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Both Fauci and Trump have dismissed speculation","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"that he does not attend some of the briefings","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"because they are on bad terms .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"In addition , Fauci now has security detail","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"after receiving threats ,","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"according to media reports .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"The expert has drawn criticism from some of Trump 's staunchest allies online","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"who accuse him of contradicting the president .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Where 's Fauci ?","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Doctor 's absence is noticed at White House coronavirus briefing","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"According to the CDC ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"\" There are no US Food and Drug Administration","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"( FDA )","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"-approved drugs specifically for the treatment of patients with COVID-19 . \"","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"The FDA ' s website also has an answer for people","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"who ask","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"if they should take chloroquine or hydroxychloroquine","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"to prevent or treat coronavirus .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"\" No , \" an answer on the FDA ' s FAQ about coronavirus says .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"\" Hydroxychloroquine and chloroquine are available in the United States by prescription only for the prevention or treatment of malaria and certain inflammatory conditions such as lupus .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"The FDA is working closely with other government agencies and academic centers","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"to determine","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"whether chloroquine can be used","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"to prevent COVID-19","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"or treat patients with mild-to-moderate COVID-19 . ''","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"Want to talk more about politics ? :","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"Join our Facebook group :","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"' Across the Aisle , Across the Nation . '","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":155,"left":0,"right":154,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":101,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":86,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":1,"right":85,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":79,"right":84,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"